question: What is the name of the player who has won the most matches, and how many rank points does this player have?
result:
players.first_name || ' ' || players.last_name as player_name, MAX(winner_matches.wins) as max_wins, rankings.ranking_points
FROM players 
JOIN (
    SELECT winner_id, COUNT(*) as wins
    FROM matches
    GROUP BY winner_id
) as winner_matches ON players.player_id = winner_matches.winner_id
JOIN rankings ON players.player_id = rankings.player_id
WHERE rankings.ranking_date = (SELECT MAX(ranking_date) FROM rankings)
GROUP BY players.player_id
ORDER BY max_wins DESC
LIMIT 1;

query: SELECT T1.name ,  T2.date_of_treatment FROM Dogs AS T1 JOIN Treatments AS T2 ON T1.dog_id  =  T2.dog_id WHERE T1.breed_code  =  ( SELECT breed_code FROM Dogs GROUP BY breed_code ORDER BY count(*) ASC LIMIT 1 )
question: List the names of the dogs of the rarest breed and the treatment dates of them.
result:
Dogs.name, Treatments.date_of_treatment
FROM Dogs 
JOIN Breeds ON Dogs.breed_code = Breeds.breed_code 
JOIN Treatments ON Dogs.dog_id = Treatments.dog_id
WHERE Breeds.breed_name = (
    SELECT breed_name FROM Breeds 
    JOIN Dogs ON Breeds.breed_code = Dogs.breed_code 
    GROUP BY Breeds.breed_code 
    HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT Dogs.dog_id) = (
        SELECT MIN(dog_count) FROM (
            SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT Dogs.dog_id) as dog_count 
            FROM Dogs 
            GROUP BY Dogs.breed_code
        )
    )
);
